{"tid":215671,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食譚仔食少過小辣嘅不如唔好食","createTime":"2017-04-24T14:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T05:12:27.000Z","uid":46940,"like":5,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d51ddb286da147ffc04afc8e0e0bcf3c74ae98","tid":215671,"uid":46940,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:27:24.000Z","msg":"今日6點放學去食譚仔，坐低無耐，隔離枱就黎左四個中學生，佢地好大聲討論緊打機同打波，之後<br />\n<br />\n阿姐黎問：「食d咩呀？」<br />\n學生A：「四碗過橋米線同凍奶茶啊！」<br />\n阿姐：「要咩勒啊？」<br />\n學生A:「errrr...十小啊。」<br />\n阿姐：「係咪全部都十小？」<br />\n學生B：「食十小咁渣，我要三小！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n學生C：「小辣有幾辣？」<br />\n學生D：「小辣好辣架！我都要三小！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  」<br />\n學生C：「咁我都三小啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n我真係睇唔過眼，食個三小辣都要講咁耐，我即刻大大聲同阿姐講：「要個豆卜、竹笙米線特辣！！！！！！！就咁多！！！！！！」<br />\n<br />\n四個學生即刻靜晒，轉個頭黎望我，對我投以仰慕嘅眼神，係呢一刻佢地感受到，佢地呢班食三小辣既凡人同我中間有段長長嘅距離，我係佢地遙不及嘅高處，傲視塵世間嘅凡人，凡人永遠唔會明食麵食到特辣嘅滋味，食麵唔食辣，不如唔好食。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申，個口頂到辣，條腸頂唔到，已經屙緊</span>"},{"pid":"766d167b0e9cf213eac3bd2262868bee9a24303e","tid":215671,"uid":46940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:29:58.000Z","msg":"邊撚個偷偷地留低負皮 出黎見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e96de0ee64e561b9d6cc8dee7841fb5eff2b15","tid":215671,"uid":46940,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:30:47.000Z","msg":"你班凡人 敢做唔敢認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2214c1af7707b3b2d2a1863db2d3c6623